# Module: tf.contrib.keras.initializers

### Module `tf.contrib.keras.initializers`



Defined in [`tensorflow/contrib/keras/api/keras/initializers/__init__.py`](https://www.github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/r1.1/tensorflow/contrib/keras/api/keras/initializers/__init__.py).

Keras built-in initializers.

## Classes

[`class Constant`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/Constant): Initializer that generates tensors initialized to a constant value.

[`class Identity`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/Identity): Initializer that generates the identity matrix.

[`class Initializer`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/Initializer): Initializer base class: all initializers inherit from this class.

[`class Ones`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/Ones): Initializer that generates tensors initialized to 1.

[`class Orthogonal`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/Orthogonal): Initializer that generates a random orthogonal matrix.

[`class RandomNormal`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/RandomNormal): Initializer that generates tensors with a normal distribution.

[`class RandomUniform`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/RandomUniform): Initializer that generates tensors with a uniform distribution.

[`class TruncatedNormal`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/TruncatedNormal): Initializer that generates a truncated normal distribution.

[`class VarianceScaling`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/VarianceScaling): Initializer capable of adapting its scale to the shape of weights.

[`class Zeros`](../../../tf/contrib/keras/initializers/Zeros): Initializer that generates tensors initialized to 0.
